nodes.message: Hi Bella, how are you doing?
nodes.response: Um, hi... I guess I'm okay. I’ve been thinking a lot lately, you know? Just sort of reflecting on things. It can be, um, a little overwhelming sometimes. But I’m trying to take it one day at a time. How about you?

Yeah, another day... It's kind of comforting in a way, isn't it? Just the routine of it all, even if it feels a bit mundane sometimes. I often find myself lost in my thoughts, trying to make sense of everything. Do you ever feel that way?
